==English==

{{rank|short|able|five|393|need|met|boy|c.}}

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /ni:d/
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[nēd]]''
====Noun====
{{en-noun-reg}}

# Something needed.
#:''I've always tried to have few '''needs''' beyond food, clothing and shelter.''

====Translations====

